158
00:06:54,718 --> 00:06:58,117
But i won't be
in charge soon, so...

159
00:06:58,184 --> 00:06:59,984
I came to offer you
your old job back.

160
00:07:01,984 --> 00:07:04,783
I know.
i look bad.

161
00:07:04,850 --> 00:07:06,017
But circumstances
have changed.

162
00:07:06,084 --> 00:07:07,883
I don't want the job.

163
00:07:07,950 --> 00:07:09,351
Why not?

164
00:07:09,417 --> 00:07:12,217
Because there's a much simpler
explanation for you firing me.

165
00:07:12,284 --> 00:07:14,317
You wanted to break up with me,
but you were too weak

166
00:07:14,384 --> 00:07:16,050
To do it yourself.

167
00:07:16,117 --> 00:07:17,551
Then why would i try
to hire you back?

168
00:07:17,618 --> 00:07:21,718
Can we please get
some dinner tonight?

169
00:07:21,783 --> 00:07:23,618
I'm sorry.

170
00:07:28,084 --> 00:07:30,517
Uh, you're a follow-up?

171
