the cockroaches.

196
00:08:40,618 --> 00:08:43,584
He can't recover.

197
00:08:47,950 --> 00:08:50,017
I'm sorry.

198
00:08:53,583 --> 00:08:55,351
How was your first day
of school?

199
00:08:56,418 --> 00:08:58,051
