239
00:10:27,483 --> 00:10:28,884
<i>just thought you'd like
to know.</i>

240
00:10:37,884 --> 00:10:39,584
Lassa fever.

241
00:10:40,650 --> 00:10:42,584
You were mad
that i withheld it last time,

242
00:10:42,650 --> 00:10:43,984
